      "title": "Creation",
      "year": "March 12, 2018",
      "medium": "Watercolor, acrylic, ink pen",
      "dimensions": "55 x 41 in.",
      "image": "/uploads/old/creation.jpg",
      "description": "Made during undergrad at a time of deep fascination with Greek mythology. A depiction of the Olympians and Atlas rendered through figures, symbols, animals, and the iconography associated with each god, a student work that laid an early foundation for the mythological thinking that would define the practice to come."
